Breakdown/Double Punch/Punch/Hiss/Scavenger/Shockwave/Pyro:




Breakdown saw weapons fire, firing off a grenade at Archangel's chest.

---

Double Punch flipped to the left, the mud passing by pathetically.  Raising 
both pinchers, he fired off two energy-singature seeking missiles off, one at 
Archangel, one at Brooder.

---

Punch, on the ground, jumped up and ran, shots knocking him to the ground.

---

Hiss sidestepped, a few shots piercing into his side, leaking mech-fluid.  

---

Pyro smashed through the woods in his tank mode, the smell of fire on him.  
Stopping, he targeted with his large cannon, firing off three fireballs at 
Steel.

---

Soundwave headed for the woods, taking out a missile launcher from subspace.


---

Scavenger crawled for the Alliance base, his foot still a little paralyzed.
